    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can You Survive Jeff the Skinner?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Jeff is a bloodthirsty faceless terror who hunts bullies, and you are his next victim.</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔪 ENTER A NIGHTMARE YOU CAN’T ESCAPE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/f36670df4c87bcacc97b7218df45eb25.poster.avif?t=1771664925\" width=630 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/f36670df4c87bcacc97b7218df45eb25.webm?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/f36670df4c87bcacc97b7218df45eb25.mp4?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of darkness and horror in the game &quot;Jeff the Skinner&quot;! Prepare yourself for an immersive and thrilling adventure inside an abandoned house, where you must find a way to escape from the merciless and terrifying Jeff. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚪 MULTIPLE WAYS TO ESCAPE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freedom is possible… if you’re smart enough. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Main Door Escape</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/003d771e7201f1413f14d9975cce433d.poster.avif?t=1771664925\" width=630 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/003d771e7201f1413f14d9975cce433d.webm?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/003d771e7201f1413f14d9975cce433d.mp4?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main door is covered with different locks and now you have to search the house and find keys and other objects to unlock the door and escape this house. Outsmart him and break out through the main door.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Escape</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/bbca9936f6cb91c39654da3cdee3b007.poster.avif?t=1771664925\" width=630 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/bbca9936f6cb91c39654da3cdee3b007.webm?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145930/extras/bbca9936f6cb91c39654da3cdee3b007.mp4?t=1771664925\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the house, there is a garage. In the garage, there is an old car. If you manage to start it and open the garage door you can escape that way. Repair and unlock the hidden vehicle to flee the nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧠 SOLVE PUZZLES TO STAY ALIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival isn’t just about running—it’s about thinking fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Puzzles:</strong><br>Unlock doors, decode hidden messages, repair broken mechanisms, and piece together the story behind Jeff the Skinner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Essential Tools:</strong><br>Find keys, crowbars, flashlights, and other items that are vital to your survival. Use them wisely—every resource matters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Terrifying Environments:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crawl through blood-stained basements, silent corridors, and decaying rooms filled with disturbing clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Save your Friend and make choices.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your friend is skinned. Will you risk everything to save him, or leave him to face a grisly fate? The choice is yours, but remember — his life depends on it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ARE YOU READY TO FACE JEFF THE SKINNER?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jeff gives you five days in the house. If you fail to escape by the final day... well, you can probably guess what awaits you then.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The house is locked.<br>Jeff the Skinner is waiting.<br>Your survival depends on your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you escape his house… or become his next victim?</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
